Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.96,0:00:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这么玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 太狡猾了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.37,0:00:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.37,0:00:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太 起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我再睡会…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.17,0:00:46.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 夏天可是很短的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.75,0:00:47.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.75,0:00:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.14,0:01:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.52,0:01:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.31,0:01:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么…怎么穿成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.77,0:01:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为啊 今天开始不就是暑假了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三四 一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三四 一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.03,0:03:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三四…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.91,0:03:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.83,0:03:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.62,0:03:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么啊 千鹤学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.54,0:03:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么啊 说起夏天自然就是广播体操吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.63,0:03:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.38,0:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 耕太也一起来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.18,0:03:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.72,0:03:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你叫我一起做　这也太…\N一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.76,0:03:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.73,0:03:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.39,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去这样 把胸部这么挤起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.94,0:03:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三四 一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三四 一二三四
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.57,0:03:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三四 嗯啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.45,0:04:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来用跳跃运动摇起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵涌啵涌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵涌啵涌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.59,0:04:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵涌啵涌 啵涌啵涌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.34,0:04:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啵涌啵涌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.80,0:04:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下去是将臀部高高抬起摆出猫咪一样的姿势
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.14,0:04:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后保持这样伸缩臀部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.64,0:04:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.48,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 耕太也一起做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是哪门子广播体操啊　明明是色情体操了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.61,0:04:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做爽了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.70,0:04:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 咱们去吃早饭吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次又在练习什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.35,0:04:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…千鹤学姐 这个是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.82,0:05:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我煎的不错吧 这对胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是练习了好久呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:16.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来嘛 吃吧吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.43,0:05:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那东西好难抓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:41.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明在眼前有这么多的饭菜材料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.60,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.98,0:05:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子瘪瘪的都使不上力气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个好天气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏日祭典吗 这次我一定要想办法挽回
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.78,0:06:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我能行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.66,0:06:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 一定得上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.00,0:06:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 忘记关了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.06,0:07:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不知道时机的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.24,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 有纪你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.74,0:07:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.91,0:07:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是你叫我出来的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.87,0:07:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.08,0:07:33.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 你瞧 暑假不是经常起不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.46,0:07:35.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是一直起不来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.51,0:07:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先去看电影吧 电影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.93,0:07:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有部想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.05,0:07:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.43,0:07:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看了就知道啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.35,0:07:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.48,0:07:59.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说我说 耕太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.28,0:08:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别做作业了 来玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行哦 在下午之前做完作业是最重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:08.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你又不是小学生了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做哪门啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.50,0:08:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在做物理作业
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.59,0:08:18.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热胀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.17,0:08:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变热之后就会变大变硬的那东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太 真下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.68,0:08:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是这种东西啊 这只是物理而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热死了 热死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把电扇开大点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真热呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤学姐 看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 看到什么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊不 那个…就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.06,0:09:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.52,0:09:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.81,0:09:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.57,0:09:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啊 耕太你热胀了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 这样都做不了作业了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.64,0:09:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.05,0:09:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心 蒲团 源氏物语
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得有点奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.69,0:10:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁啊 选的这些书
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:10.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好饿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.05,0:10:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那片云彩在我眼中变成鲜奶油了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.89,0:10:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种奢侈品 会把肚子吃坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那在莲的眼中 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看起来 像凉拌豆腐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.49,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉拌豆腐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.16,0:10:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是奢侈品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.82,0:10:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行李 不重吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行李果然还是给我拿的好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.05,0:11:13.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己的份会好好拿着的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 但累了要说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.68,0:11:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.19,0:11:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你们俩这是要去旅行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.11,0:11:23.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好传达到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.03,0:11:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来你们两位是这样的关系啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.74,0:11:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.91,0:11:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪她无家可归 所以才和我一起回故乡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.66,0:11:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对 绝对不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.16,0:11:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这么坚决地否定好吗 桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.84,0:11:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是的 那个…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.46,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要和澪一起  那个…这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.18,0:11:53.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很开心…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桐山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.81,0:11:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 怎么都好 回家路上小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要随时小心别做些会露馅的事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.69,0:12:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.40,0:12:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.44,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.82,0:12:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼光可是不会错的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是有纪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.70,0:12:15.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么接下去干嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:19.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我肚子饿了 去吃饭吧 吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.71,0:12:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:28.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来我也饿了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,午饭怎么解决
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天果然是吃素面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,素面吗 好主意哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说道素面的话 自然是流水素面了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.23,0:12:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吃流水素面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.48,0:12:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 没有准备啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.44,0:12:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 稍微等下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.36,0:12:50.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在先去浴室把身体洗洗干净
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.90,0:12:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过会记得来哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗澡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.20,0:12:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤学姐 我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边已经准备好了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.75,0:13:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 进来吧 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.17,0:13:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.21,0:13:12.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到千鹤的流水素面店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什什什什什什什…么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.64,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.69,0:13:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来耕太 到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.31,0:13:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐在这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.69,0:13:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来我示范给你看哟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啊 耕太 好好看了没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.34,0:13:58.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 啊没
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 千鹤的流水素面开始了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.69,0:14:07.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 耕太赶紧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 掉下去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.98,0:14:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.24,0:14:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太 不是那里啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.83,0:14:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.83,0:14:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是觉得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.71,0:14:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看啦 都掉下去了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.80,0:14:41.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太 机会!就是现在啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.93,0:14:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行的啦不行的啦不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不要 不行不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.77,0:14:52.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太 快点拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.15,0:14:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤 已经不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.66,0:15:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不行了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.49,0:15:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太 等下啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.54,0:15:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.34,0:15:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不开
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:46.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.05,0:16:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好烫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.60,0:16:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么啊 又弄糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷 冷气好像开太足了吧 这边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.09,0:16:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:48.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.81,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才是呢 在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 我…我出来买东西的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.86,0:17:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.86,0:17:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝比奈为什么会在这里?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边 图书馆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 是这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.63,0:17:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.33,0:17:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 小豆汤啦 是机器弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.92,0:17:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不喝吗 那能给我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.93,0:17:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体稍稍有些冷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.81,0:17:29.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 请喝请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天喝小豆汤算是别有风味的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.94,0:17:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不算是啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:45.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有纪对这种东西有兴趣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.58,0:17:53.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前就想要了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.54,0:17:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就买下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.59,0:17:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想买的话就也不是买不起了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,压岁钱和零花钱全用完了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.72,0:18:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.09,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借我点钱～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.51,0:18:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 果然有呢 独角仙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.44,0:18:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在家乡的时候经常抓的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.90,0:18:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么抓一个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.24,0:18:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.28,0:18:27.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太的肩膀借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.16,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有必要这样做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.21,0:18:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么上了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.13,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得可靠不少了呢 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.26,0:18:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 千鹤学姐 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.23,0:19:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.19,0:19:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像很不错…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:12.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.12,0:19:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑油油的又粗又弯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 好淫荡啊 千鹤学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.29,0:19:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜甜的真好吃呢 苍蝇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.63,0:19:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这还真是上天的恩惠啊 身体内充满了能量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.26,0:19:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.89,0:19:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 你们俩
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天开始就什么都没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.40,0:19:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子好饿 肚子好饿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.15,0:19:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.15,0:19:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 不介意的话 我家的冰箱里有剩下的素面
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:55.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.54,0:19:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 钥匙给你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.46,0:20:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够惨的呢 那两个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～呀 真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.35,0:20:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小桐 好可爱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 这样很危险的啦 有纪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.06,0:20:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真坏错啊 这张脸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.19,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.57,0:20:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.24,0:20:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边也没锁着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.41,0:20:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是粗心大意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.46,0:20:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过正好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进去等他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.55,0:20:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.26,0:20:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就到这吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 朝比奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.10,0:21:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.81,0:21:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:07.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.98,0:21:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天 对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…还在生气吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.33,0:21:18.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们来干什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.10,0:21:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来看看女儿有什么不可以的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.18,0:21:42.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没啥事的话就赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.98,0:21:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么口气啊 千鹤大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.19,0:21:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,边吃刨冰边说这话可是完全没说服力的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是没办法的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.78,0:21:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是雪女啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 耕太 好久不见了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.28,0:21:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好 好久不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.87,0:22:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶紧给我滚回雪山里去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.83,0:22:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦 千鹤学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.66,0:22:06.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就到你家去吧 带个路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.84,0:22:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多由良同学 我把这个拿过去了哟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是 你们到底是过来干什么的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.43,0:22:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.18,0:22:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.14,0:22:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.32,0:22:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话还请穿穿看呢 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.32,0:22:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 多谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:37.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在打啥主意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.74,0:22:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这孩子 真是的 没啥主意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.70,0:22:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真合身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.79,0:22:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.54,0:22:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的也很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.59,0:22:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身呢 千鹤学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.55,0:22:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.68,0:23:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么明天就穿这个去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.14,0:23:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有烟花的吗 明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.39,0:23:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 想得挺周到的嘛 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.31,0:23:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你得一个人去哟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.86,0:23:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为耕太得和我一起去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.53,0:23:18.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会变成这样的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说到底是怎么回事啊 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.12,0:23:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烟花啊 好的 明天一定！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.00,0:23:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前就约定好的了是吧 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这回事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.55,0:23:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真冷淡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.46,0:23:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊 耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.05,0:23:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鹤大人 就按夫人说的做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.22,0:23:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.76,0:23:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耕太
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:48.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你这狼啊 别趁乱抱过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 耕太 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.81,0:23:51.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.77,0:23:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都给我离远点啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}真假鸳鸯谱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:28.33,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,窓に写る二人の影が
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:33.96,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踊るように 揺れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:39.21,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑いながら 手を取り合って
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光の向こう 歩き出した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:50.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キラリ☆眩しい胸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:57.02,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,揺らす出来事が始まるの
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:02:07.83,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人への階段 まだまだ焦らず二人で
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:09.20,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:15.17,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミが居るから 過ごす日々さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:19.09,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも 輝いて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:28.05,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心にそっとしまった宝物 それは
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.35,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋の始まり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:28.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照在窗子上的两个人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:33.96,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛如在翩翩起舞般 摇曳不止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.33,0:01:39.21,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互携起手 一边笑着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:45.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一边向光芒的对岸迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.14,0:01:50.39,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪闪发光的耀眼的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:57.02,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦摇动就会发生种种风波嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.02,0:02:07.83,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迈向成人的楼梯 两个人一起慢慢地走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.49,0:02:09.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wish you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:15.17,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为有你在 度过的每一天才会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.42,0:02:19.09,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直都闪耀不止
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.55,0:02:28.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深藏于心中的宝物 那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.47,0:02:31.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋爱的开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:24:00.28,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来へと続いてゆく道
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:06.16,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人なら 歩いてゆけるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:12.04,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見つめ合うまなざしの向こう側
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:18.17,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠の絆が見えるの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:31.06,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この場所であなたに恋したあの瞬間(とき)から
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:35.60,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界が変わったようなキセキ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.31,0:24:42.82,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ほんの小さなことで 感じられる幸せ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.28,0:24:47.78,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝石箱を大切に開けるの
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:53.70,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,そっと 優しい光りが差し込む
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.25,0:24:59.29,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あなたといる今が とても嬉しくて
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.84,0:25:11.10,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸せの風に包まれて いつだって あなたのとなりに
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:16.98,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんな日もきっと笑顔になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.56,0:25:23.03,edjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運命の恋を信じてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.06,0:24:00.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与未来相连接的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.94,0:24:06.16,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人一起的话 一定能够前进的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:12.04,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互凝视的视线的另一边
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.62,0:24:18.17,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够看到永远的羁绊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.51,0:24:31.06,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许是这个地方在与你相恋的时候开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.56,0:24:35.60,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经变成了能够改变世界的奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.31,0:24:42.82,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使再小也能感受到的幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.28,0:24:47.78,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心地放入宝石箱里
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.37,0:24:53.70,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不经意间 柔和的光线已经射入
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.25,0:24:59.29,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的如今 是多么的令人开心
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.84,0:25:11.10,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被幸福的风所包围 无论何时都能在你的边上
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.56,0:25:16.98,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是什么样的日子 一定都能是笑脸的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.56,0:25:23.03,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我相信命运的恋情

